message:
Hello everyone, 

We are doing a survey to help us create an application that can help people schedule and organize getting together activities with their friends. 

The survey only takes 2-3 minutes and its super easy to answer. Please share if you like the idea and want this application to happen.
story: Nour Eldin Ali shared a link to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Google Forms - create and analyze surveys, for free.
caption: accounts.google.com
description: Create a new survey on your own or with others at the same time. Choose from a variety of survey types and analyze results in Google Forms. Free from Google.
